lass=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 04, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rob1665703136198.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rob1665703136198.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rob1665703136198.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rob1665703136198\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rob1665703136198__uputmess_408473\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Put a message in the Uniface message frame.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rob1665703136198__topic_d123662e1_d123663e1_d123664e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rob1665703136198_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rob1665703136198__codeblock_s43_2fk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">void uputmess (unsigned char*message);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rob1665703136198__topic_d87367e1_d87368e1_d87369e1_d87370e1_d87371e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d947704e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"rob1665703136198__parml_m1g_gfk_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">message</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">String containing the message to send</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rob1665703136198__topic_d87372e1_d87373e1_d87374e1_d87375e1_d87376e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d947704e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rob1665703136198__p_d123677e1_d123678e1_d123679e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uputmess</code> does not return a\n            value.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rob1665703136198__topic_d87377e1_d87378e1_d87379e1_d87380e1_d87381e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d947704e91\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rob1665703136198__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rob1665703136198__topic_d87382e1_d87383e1_d87384e1_d87385e1_d87386e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d947704e104\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rob1665703136198__p_d123689e1_d123690e1_d123691e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uputmess</code> copies the text in\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">message</var> to the Uniface message frame. To create separate lines,\n            you must use a carriage return (CR, ASCII code 13) as the line separator rather than a\n            line feed (LF, ASCII code 10). If you pass a long text without line separators, Uniface\n            will break lines after 1024 characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rob1665703136198__p_d123692e1_d123693e1_d123694e1\">Note that, because the line separator is a CR, not\n            a LF, you cannot dump the contents of a text file to the message frame. You must read\n            the individual lines, remove the line separators, and call <code class=\"ph codeph\">uputmess</code> on\n            every line, as shown in the example.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rob1665703136198__section_aqx_3fk_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d947704e124\">Example</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example reads lines from a file and writes them to the\n            Uniface message frame one by one:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104rob1665703136198_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"rob1665703136198__codeblock_obp_kfk_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\n#include &lt;ctype.h&gt;\n\nEXPORT void FileToMessFrame()\n{\nFILE* fp;\nchar line[81];\nchar* p;\n\n\nfp = fopen(\"myfile.txt\", \"r\");\nwhile ( fgets(line, 81, fp) )\n{\nfor ( p=line; isprint(*p); p++ );\n*p = 0;\nuputmess(line);\n}\nfclose(fp);\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531706\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uputmess Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 04, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Put a message in the Uniface message frame. Explain this code void uputmess (unsigned char*message); Copy Parameters message String containing the message to send Return Values uputmess does not return a value. Use Library: yrtl Description uputmess copies the text in message to the Uniface message frame. To create separate lines, you must use a carriage return (CR, ASCII code 13) as the line separator rather than a line feed (LF, ASCII code 10). If you pass a long text without line separators, Uniface will break lines after 1024 characters. Note that, because the line separator is a CR, not a LF, you cannot dump the contents of a text file to the message frame. You must read the individual lines, remove the line separators, and call uputmess on every line, as shown in the example. Example The following example reads lines from a file and writes them to the Uniface message frame one by one: Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> #include <stdio.h> #include <ctype.h> EXPORT void FileToMessFrame() { FILE* fp; char line[81]; char* p; fp = fopen(\"myfile.txt\", \"r\"); while ( fgets(line, 81, fp) ) { for ( p=line; isprint(*p); p++ ); *p = 0; uputmess(line); } fclose(fp); } Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}